{"tid":1164113,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"出去影相，試過唔見乜","createTime":"2019-05-21T00:25:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T04:01:57.000Z","uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"42fe62f7994b167cb3528142b188a17877894280","tid":1164113,"uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:25:25.000Z","msg":"我講先，是啤電，遮光罩，夾埋唔見左5舊幾水，真正體驗咩叫散紙黎姐，跌都跌左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n平時好慳，一個飯分2餐食為左慳錢，咁樣唔見野法好肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e355e68870392eeb7902a235a0737babb28f5af5","tid":1164113,"uid":14535,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:46:44.000Z","msg":"聽講好似有人影相（定唔知過度沉迷器材）<br />\n然後唔見咗條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a364c691fbb98a1426da1b3c1077446f80a304","tid":1164113,"uid":227174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:05:08.000Z","msg":"接目環 2個<br />\n相機電 1粒<br />\n冇了"},{"pid":"1bb5e77b3cae19e451917e12042cdb1ea4e3e569","tid":1164113,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:06:48.000Z","msg":"唔見形象<br />\n唔見女朋友"},{"pid":"3ae38c6530c4a678b0e19394db9c3b30f360e67b","tid":1164113,"uid":152840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"nd filter, 千幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9837ac07140056dd99700cd525e2c3c83cef647","tid":1164113,"uid":45252,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T06:23:02.000Z","msg":"鏡頭蓋<br />\n由吳哥窟頂掉左落去，見到響度但爬唔到上去拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n燈泡頭既鏡頭蓋，最後2百幾買返"},{"pid":"94c5b39358464f5fc356bc8311b4f361cb15a005","tid":1164113,"uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e355e68870392eeb7902a235a0737babb28f5af